org.dmontagnese.changeMaker.domain

Class CoinCount

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dmontagnese.changeMaker.domain.CoinCount

  • public class CoinCount
extends java.lang.Object
    A bean that is instantiated and returned to the client containing the computed values appropriate to a dollar_amount The class is an ORM Entity ( Hibernate ) that, along with being returned to the client, is cached in the database
